We recommended that Management requires the GAD Focal Point System to:

Attend seminars on GAD particularly those involved in the Focal Point System;

Institutionalize the GAD database with adequate and systematically gathered sex-disaggregated data which will provide the bases for gender analysis, planning, programming and policy formation;

